'From Squeak2.7 of 5 January 2000 [latest update: #1789] on 5 February 2000 at 12:49:19 pm'!"Change Set:		1001PopUpMenuFix-smaDate:			5 February 2000Author:			Stefan Matthias AustIn MVC, sometimes a popup menu was wrongly displayed in the topLeft corner of the screen instead of near the cursor."!!PopUpMenu methodsFor: 'private' stamp: 'sma 2/5/2000 11:56'!rescan	"Cause my form to be recomputed after a font change."	labelString == nil ifTrue: [labelString _ 'NoText!!'].	self labels: labelString font: (MenuStyle fontAt: 1) lines: lineArray.	frame _ marker _ form _ nil.	"PopUpMenu allSubInstancesDo: [:m | m rescan]"! !